Articles.Content:
I am having a fatal/gamebreaking error that comes with B9 Part Switch, which most CKAN mods rely upon, and it follows with something of this:

Fatal exception while loading fields on module ModuleB9PartSwitch on part
Exception while loading field subtypes on type B9PartSwitch.ModuleB9PartSwitch
Exception while loading fields on subtype PartSubtype LiquidFuel
Exception while loading field tankType on type B9PartSwitch.PartSubtype
The tank definitions have not been loaded yet (done after game database load).
This is likely caused by an earlier error or by ModuleManager being missing or out of date

 

I have verified files, made sure every mod I needed was up-to-date, and I don't know what to do next

thanks if you can help!
